OL,3,CPaedophile handed more than 16 year
OL,4,Cprison sentence for a decade of abuse
OL,6,FA Jersey paedophile has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 16 and a half years in prison for
OL,8,Fsexual offences against a child
OL,9,Fincluding attempted rape.
OL,11,FRichard Louis Romeril, 49, appeared in
OL,12,FJersey Royal Court on Friday 29
OL,13,FNovember to be sentenced for 10 sexual
OL,14,Foffences he had been found guilty of
OL,15,Fby trial in June.
OL,17,FThis was in addition to four other
OL,18,Foffences he'd pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Frelating to making indecent and
OL,20,Fprohibited images of children.
