OL,3,CPaedophile handed more than 16 year
OL,4,Cprison sentence for a decade of abuse
OL,6,FRomeril committed the offences between
OL,7,FMarch 2011 and March 2022, where he
OL,8,Fhad subjected a child to sexual abuse.
OL,10,FThe abuse is understood to have
OL,11,Fhappened almost weekly, progressively
OL,12,Fgetting worse over time, and resulting
OL,13,Fin the attempted rape of his victim.
OL,15,FStates of Jersey Police have commended
OL,16,Fthe victim for her bravery in speaking
OL,17,Fout over their abuse.
