OL,6,FDetective Constable Sian Dupre
OL,7,Fprovided a statement saying: "The
OL,8,Fsentence handed to Richard Romeril
OL,9,Ftoday reflects the gravity of his
OL,10,Fcrime and their profound impact.
OL,12,F"We want to recognise the
OL,13,Fextraordinary bravery of the survivor
OL,14,Fwho courageously came forward to make
OL,15,Fthe complaint. Their remarkable
OL,16,Fstrength and resilience have been
OL,17,Fpivotal in bringing Romeril to justice
OL,18,Ftoday.
